comment: [Observable in enhanced video] LHH shows Clarkson (LAL) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Nance Jr. (LAL) firms up and sets the screen on Butler (CHI), giving him room to avoid the contact.
Lopez (CHI) and Randle (LAL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor (Chicago ball) was upheld.
Ingram (LAL) makes contact with Butler (CHI) that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Rondo (CHI) makes body to body contact with Randle (LAL) that affects his ability to secure the ball.
Randle (LAL) makes marginal contact with Mirotic (CHI) on the perimeter.
Randle (LAL) and Wade (CHI) make incidental contact with one another following the made shot. Wade falls to the floor and makes incidental contact with Nance Jr. (LAL).
Williams (LAL) sets the screen on Butler (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Nance Jr. (LAL) sets the screen on Rondo (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Rondo (CHI) makes contact with Williams' (LAL) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Rondo (CHI) calls the timeout within 5 seconds.
Lopez (CHI) sets the screen and extends his arms into Ingram (LAL) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor (Lakers ball) was upheld.
Ingram (LAL) does not step OOB after receiving the inbound pass.
Grant (CHI) commits a take foul on Randle (LAL).
Mirotic (CHI) commits a take foul on Nance Jr. (LAL).
